name: River of Mind
description:
Sometimes a person can just get lost in their thoughts, like a river flowing through time and space. Sometimes those thoughts change over time, as we pass through various stages in our life. Each thought can be stone in that stream of consciousness, each stage a bend in the river of the mind.

Do I know where this creative journey will take me? There are so many different styles to explore. But with each piece I mint, it's like a thought in that stream and each style I explore, a bend in that creative river.
